257
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:47,163
To Sheriff Purdy...

258
00:31:47,405 --> 00:31:49,498
...of Chloride.

259
00:31:49,674 --> 00:31:53,007
Believe hostiles...

260
00:31:53,177 --> 00:31:56,271
