266
00:32:13,865 --> 00:32:19,599
l'll send the undertaker out...

267
00:32:19,771 --> 00:32:23,468
-...for the remains.
-You're not going after them?

268
00:32:24,776 --> 00:32:27,108
Not under the present
circumstances, ma'am.

269
00:32:27,278 --> 00:32:30,441
With the fair in town, l need
all the men l have right here.

270
00:32:30,615 --> 00:32:33,140
lf you don't follow now,
their trail will get cold.

271
00:32:33,318 --> 00:32:34,979
The Army is handling the situation.

272
00:32:35,153 --> 00:32:38,452
They have Apache scouts.
