273
00:32:38,623 --> 00:32:41,387
lf someone doesn't go now,
my daughter may be dead.

274
00:32:43,061 --> 00:32:47,555
Ma'am, l am elected to keep vigil
over this town of ours.

275
00:32:47,732 --> 00:32:51,395
Just one or two men, sir,
that's all l'm asking.

276
00:32:52,003 --> 00:32:54,471
Ma'am, l am sorry.

277
00:32:55,073 --> 00:32:57,906
Seth, l need a word with you.

278
00:32:59,243 --> 00:33:01,507
lt was the lndians did it.

279
00:33:02,780 --> 00:33:07,479
Now, ladies, l will not authorize
fireworks until a water wagon is here.

280
00:33:09,153 --> 00:33:12,020
Ma'am, that's the drunkard
from last night.

281
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:14,488
What would you like me
to do with him?

282
00:33:14,792 --> 00:33:17,124
Let him go.

283
