295
00:34:19,657 --> 00:34:21,420
Hush, hush.

296
00:34:22,927 --> 00:34:24,292
Hush, now. lt's all right.

297
00:34:33,571 --> 00:34:35,061
Hush.

298
00:34:49,387 --> 00:34:52,254
The Army's headed
