-Damn well looks lndian to me.

393
00:47:43,594 --> 00:47:45,186
No, he's a....

394
00:47:48,732 --> 00:47:49,960
That's my father.

395
00:47:51,835 --> 00:47:56,033
l've been hoping we'd find you, sir.
We need your help.

396
00:47:57,774 --> 00:48:00,971
We tracked my daughter
south from Chloride.

397
00:48:01,144 --> 00:48:03,305
They're heading toward Mexico.

398
00:48:04,047 --> 00:48:05,514
